---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Vision - OrionHealth"
  description="Our mission: Preparing your health data for the AI revolution in personalized medicine"
  lang="en"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-16 md:py-32">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h1 class="section-title font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase mb-6 md:mb-8" data-animate>
        OUR <span class="text-accent">VISION</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-bone mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" data-animate>
        Preparing your health data for the <span class="text-accent">AI revolution</span> in personalized medicine
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-80" data-animate>
        We believe the future of healthcare is local-first, AI-powered, and patient-owned. OrionHealth is building the foundation today.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Statement -->
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-charcoal/30">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-5xl">
      <div class="glass p-6 md:p-12 rounded-2xl" data-animate>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-bone mb-6">
          üéØ Mission Statement
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-bone-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          OrionHealth exists to give individuals complete ownership and control of their health data,
          while preparing that data for the next generation of AI-powered personalized medicine.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-bone-dark leading-relaxed">
          We believe healthcare is too important to be locked in corporate silos. Your health journey
          is uniquely yours, and your data should work for you‚Äînot against you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline: The 5 Phases -->
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 px-4">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="section-title font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase text-center mb-12 md:mb-16" data-animate>
        THE <span class="text-accent">ROADMAP</span>
      </h2>

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-16 pb-12 border-l-2 border-accent/30" data-animate>
        <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent border-4 border-charcoal"></div>
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-accent border border-accent/30 uppercase tracking-wider">
              Phase 1 ‚Ä¢ 2025
            </span>
            <span class="text-xs text-bone-dark opacity-60 uppercase">Current</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">
            üìã Data Collection & Ownership
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Build a robust, private system for storing health records locally. Users can upload documents,
            lab results, prescriptions, and medical images‚Äîall encrypted and stored only on their device.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-accent/10 text-accent">‚úì Isar Database</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-accent/10 text-accent">‚úì Local Storage</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-accent/10 text-accent">‚úì File Management</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-accent/10 text-accent">‚úì OCR Support</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-16 pb-12 border-l-2 border-accent/30" data-animate>
        <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent/50 border-4 border-charcoal"></div>
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-accent border border-accent/30 uppercase tracking-wider">
              Phase 2 ‚Ä¢ 2025-2026
            </span>
            <span class="text-xs text-secondary opacity-80 uppercase">In Progress</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">
            üß† On-Device AI Intelligence
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Integrate local Large Language Models (LLMs) to analyze health records. Users can chat with
            their data, get insights, and receive basic health guidance‚Äîall without sending data to the cloud.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-secondary/10 text-secondary">‚öôÔ∏è ONNX Runtime</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-secondary/10 text-secondary">‚öôÔ∏è RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-accent/10 text-accent">‚úì Chat Interface</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-accent/10 text-accent">‚úì Vector Search</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-16 pb-12 border-l-2 border-accent/30" data-animate>
        <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-bone/20 border-4 border-charcoal"></div>
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl opacity-80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark border border-bone/20 uppercase tracking-wider">
              Phase 3 ‚Ä¢ 2026-2027
            </span>
            <span class="text-xs text-bone-dark opacity-40 uppercase">Planned</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">
            üî¨ Health Pattern Recognition
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Advanced AI models detect patterns across your historical health data. Identify trends,
            anomalies, and potential health risks early‚Äîempowering proactive healthcare decisions.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">Time-series Analysis</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">Anomaly Detection</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">Risk Scoring</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 4 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-16 pb-12 border-l-2 border-accent/30" data-animate>
        <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-bone/20 border-4 border-charcoal"></div>
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl opacity-60">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark border border-bone/20 uppercase tracking-wider">
              Phase 4 ‚Ä¢ 2027-2028
            </span>
            <span class="text-xs text-bone-dark opacity-40 uppercase">Future</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">
            ü§ù Interoperability & Standards
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Connect with healthcare providers via FHIR (Fast Healthcare Interoperability Resources) and
            other standards. Import data from hospitals, labs, and wearables‚Äîwhile keeping control local.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">FHIR Integration</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">HL7 Support</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">Wearable Sync</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 5 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-16" data-animate>
        <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-bone/20 border-4 border-charcoal"></div>
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl opacity-60">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark border border-bone/20 uppercase tracking-wider">
              Phase 5 ‚Ä¢ 2028+
            </span>
            <span class="text-xs text-bone-dark opacity-40 uppercase">Vision</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">
            üåç Personalized Medicine Revolution
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Your comprehensive health history becomes the foundation for truly personalized treatments.
            AI models can recommend interventions tailored to your unique biology, lifestyle, and history.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">Genomic Integration</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">Drug Interactions</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bone/10 text-bone-dark">Treatment Optimization</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Matters -->
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-charcoal/30 to-transparent">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="section-title font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase text-center mb-12" data-animate>
        WHY THIS <span class="text-accent">MATTERS</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl" data-animate>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üè•</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">Healthcare is Fragmented</h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Your health data is scattered across hospitals, labs, doctors' offices, and apps.
            No one has the complete picture‚Äîexcept you should.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl" data-animate>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üîí</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">Privacy is Non-Negotiable</h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Medical data breaches affect millions yearly. The only truly secure data is data that
            never leaves your device in the first place.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl" data-animate>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ü§ñ</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">AI is Coming to Healthcare</h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Future AI models will need your complete health history to provide personalized insights.
            Start collecting that data now‚Äîon your terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <div class="glass p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl" data-animate>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üå±</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-bone mb-3">Open Source Builds Trust</h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-bone-dark leading-relaxed">
            When your health is on the line, you need to trust the tools you use. Open source
            means transparency, auditability, and community-driven development.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-32 px-4">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-bone mb-6" data-animate>
        Join the <span class="text-accent">Movement</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-bone-dark mb-8" data-animate>
        OrionHealth is open source and community-driven. Help us build the future of patient-owned healthcare.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center" data-animate>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/iberi22/OrionHealth"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-primary px-8 py-4 text-sm"
        >
          ‚≠ê Star on GitHub
        </a>
        <a
          href="/#download"
          class="btn-secondary px-8 py-4 text-sm"
        >
          üì± Download App
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .glass {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  [data-animate] {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  @keyframes fade-in-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
